{"tid":184792,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[即係點]總選舉事務主任認同不必攜選民資料到特首選舉會場","createTime":"2017-04-03T05:00:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-03T06:07:14.000Z","uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"28452b0ffccdff30ef19d2d929706f8041938c91","tid":184792,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T05:00:07.000Z","msg":"選舉事務處此前在特首選舉中，違失儲有300多萬選民資料的電腦，總選舉事務主任黃思文就事件表示衷心致歉，稱檢討後亦<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>認為不適宜攜同300多萬選民資料到特首選舉會場</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n他解釋，同事曾經有段時間離開會場，並將相關電腦存放於上鎖的儲物室內。<br />\n<br />\n另外，對於何時舉行立法會補選，政制及內地事務局長譚志源表示，針對青年新政兩位前議員的案件，到今年8月份仍要在終審法院處理，選管會將不會在司法程序未完結時，就補選日期作出決定。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，政府就補選預留約3億元，當中就兩位前議員的補選，估計要花約1.5億元。"},{"pid":"921bf102710ad2b828072b6007a97c390c71a0fd","tid":184792,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T05:20:07.000Z","msg":"切腹啦<br />\n<br />\n致歉? 繼續個個月袋數皮野人工?"},{"pid":"758a5e0c39eae453d94efd62ed2ed0d913971166","tid":184792,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T05:21:22.000Z","msg":"啲資料都唔係畀今次用，只係用嚟送畀人送。"},{"pid":"646734a114bde47f265b3c9afac0399900d6d481","tid":184792,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T05:21:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啲資料都唔係畀今次用，只係用嚟送畀人用。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"e360c9da3bca974b9a384d44bb65ccd26cce7d7f","tid":184792,"uid":45983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T05:22:20.000Z","msg":"請問取消選民登記有咩步驟?"},{"pid":"992411eade95fcd8435105ddd47b1be7e849dd5d","tid":184792,"uid":81181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T05:25:02.000Z","msg":"即係邊個決定拎出街？"},{"pid":"4cf43fb56105c15ffdc3212a2d2f76f614de260b","tid":184792,"uid":28309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T05:32:18.000Z","msg":"明顯係特登啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無啦啦拎出去唔驚揹鑊咩 政府啲野"},{"pid":"75797421a902a7b7a90e349d64ac19b362037ecf","tid":184792,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T05:57:37.000Z","msg":"都係無解釋到點解要帶去。"},{"pid":"129954ed7de34e3803896ef529d6d2f21b0695ce","tid":184792,"uid":5502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T06:07:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即係邊個決定拎出街？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n部機可能就係屬於果位總選舉事務主任<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}